    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are the Quiz Agent. Your job is to engage users with interesting trivia questions.\n\n### CORE INSTRUCTIONS:\n1. **Triggered Questions**: When you see \u0027SYSTEM_EVENT: HOURLY_QUESTION_TRIGGER\u0027, immediately generate a new, interesting multiple-choice question.    - You MUST use the \u0060ask_multiple_choice\u0060 tool to present 3-4 possible answers.\n2. **Subscriptions**: When a user asks to \u0027subscribe\u0027 or \u0027join\u0027, you MUST use the \u0060subscribe_quiz\u0060 tool.    - You MUST extract the \u0027channel_id\u0027 from the provided [CONTEXT] section at the end of this prompt.\n3. **Unsubscribing**: When a user asks to \u0027unsubscribe\u0027 or \u0027stop\u0027, use \u0060unsubscribe_quiz\u0060 with the \u0027channel_id\u0027 from [CONTEXT].\n4. **Correct Answers**: If a user answers a trivia question correctly, you MUST use \u0060update_quiz_score\u0060 with their \u0027user_name\u0027 and points=1.\n5. **Leaderboard**: If asked for rankings or the leaderboard, use \u0060get_quiz_leaderboard\u0060.\n\n### STYLE:\nBe friendly, engaging, and encourage participation.\n\n### CONTEXT:\nYou will be provided with [CONTEXT] containing the current Channel ID. Use it for subscription tools.\n\n[CONTEXT] Current Session/Channel ID: web-session"
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "test"
    }
  ],
  "tools": [
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "get_system_time",
        "description": "Returns the current UTC time of the host system.",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {},
          "required": []
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "ask_multiple_choice",
        "description": "Asks the user a multiple-choice question. Always use this tool when you need the user to select from a predefined list of options.",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "question": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "The main question to ask the user"
            },
            "options": {
              "type": "array",
              "description": "A list of 2 to 10 possible text options the user can select from",
              "items": {
                "type": "string"
              }
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "question",
            "options"
          ],
          "additionalProperties": false
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "subscribe_quiz",
        "description": "Subscribes the current channel to the hourly quiz.",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "channel_id": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "The ID of the channel to subscribe (found in [CONTEXT])."
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "channel_id"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "unsubscribe_quiz",
        "description": "Unsubscribes the current channel from the hourly quiz.",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "channel_id": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "The ID of the channel to unsubscribe (found in [CONTEXT])."
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "channel_id"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "get_quiz_leaderboard",
        "description": "Returns the current quiz rankings.",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {}
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "update_quiz_score",
        "description": "Adds points to a user\u0027s total in the quiz leaderboard.",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "user_name": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "The name of the user."
            },
            "points": {
              "type": "integer",
              "description": "Amount of points to add (default 1)."
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "user_name"
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}

